page.title: 16WILD FLOWERS (1)
page.content: Our school, Ingrebourne J.M.&I., have studied the Western part of our area.It is mostly countryside so we decided to study all the plants and wildlife we could find. We had some help from an expert who works for our borough of Havering. Here is our list of wild plants. *=Rare ** or *** means rarer still.
